      <title>优胜美地特许经营问题不断涌现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/in-yosemite-national-park-aramark-s-problems-keep-piling-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[啮齿动物的侵扰和历史悠久的酒店的关闭使公园特许经营商 Aramark 面临的麻烦又添新气象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/in-yosemite-national-park-aramark-s-problems-keep-piling-up</guid>
